Responsibilities :-

Develop and maintain infrastructure front office platform to improve efficiency in pricing and risk management;
Integrate in house pricing library, build and maintain front office platform.

Requirements

Degree in Science/ Engineering in Mathematics, Computer Science, Physics;
Minimum 3 years' relevant experience ;
Highly goal driven and work well in fast pace environment;
Team player who is also able to work independently;
Positive work attitude and compliant to Organization policies;
Meticulous and Quality conscious.

Desired Skills and Experience
Front Office, Investment Strategies, Derivatives, Physics, Mathematics, Risk Management, Good Communication Skills, Portfolio Management, Python, Econometrics, Statistics, Pricing, Databases, Able To Work Independently, C++
